description.en:
YF Moonshot (YFMS) is a DeFi protocol which allows users to stake their cryptocurrency assets in various different pools and earn YFMS, our platforms governance token in exchange.
Users that hold & stake $YFMS will earn additional $YFMS overtime.
Users may also stake stable coins including USDT, DAI, TUSD tokens to different pools available to farm $YFMS.
